{"tid":728774,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Galaxy S9+ 用家投訴　指手機亂發相片至聯絡人","createTime":"2018-07-04T04:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T04:24:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc90dc885d04a2ae325b16f0d5a2a411caee16d7","tid":728774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"外國有三星(Samsung)手機Galaxy S9+用家在網上貼文，抱怨手機內私人照片被自動隨機發送至通訊錄聯絡人。據稱，這個問題會影響三星Galaxy S9+、S9及Note8智能手機。澳洲三星公司表示正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n在外國網上討論區Reddit，以及三星用家論壇上，都有人報告三星手機出現上述首次發生的錯漏。其中一名男士上周三(6月27日)在Reddit發文指出，他的Galaxy S9+手機在凌晨約2時半他正在睡覺時，擅自將手機內整個相片圖庫發送給他的女朋友，但在三星通訊應用程式Messages上卻沒有發送紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n網民十分關注事件，都很擔心自己會中招，有人憂慮相片亂發會引爆婚姻炸彈，亦有人則搞笑地說，「S9系列手機是否奉送離婚律師服務？」<br />\n<br />\n澳洲三星發言人證實該公司正調查這問題，但尚未核實這是否故障，以及澳洲用家是否會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n有疑難解答人員推測，該問題可能是由手機電信業者設定更新，及三星通訊應用程式Messages引起。<br />\n<br />\n一些手機用戶建議更改手機的默認短訊服務、使用Android通訊應用程式，並撤銷三星通訊應用程式Messages訪問媒體的權限，以避免發生以上問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，三星Note8手機早前亦有用家投訴稱，他排期發送的短訊傳給了錯誤的收件人。"},{"pid":"54347fe9f8d12ab90c887882c6524be4f8557f01","tid":728774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180704/s00005/1530671645102?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180704%2Fs00005%2F1530671645102%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=Eb0W3O0KtXZ08nsU8PCOagHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4701b775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180704%2Fs00005%2F1530671645102%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=e82e6660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180704/s00005/1530671645102?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"3e4e5be5aed6f3a8b6ee6daac454c5d7afa0e012","tid":728774,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"香港有冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf5b45b3d9ffc439c430b6afd83cd39fa79e72b","tid":728774,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"仲會自動發送相片去中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3cdd8fb1384e082ec1321517339db6d0f521a2","tid":728774,"uid":127611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"女友好大嫌疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}